{"tid":51305,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美杜蟲藥3450元一粒 貴英國200倍","createTime":"2016-12-23T06:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T07:29:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50367a686b9fe9f247c22ba23318db803bc02992","tid":51305,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161220/s00014/1482172116765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161220%2Fs00014%2F1482172116765&d=HT%2BmosxtFQmebK13LlDikn8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=ec7ffb47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161220%2Fs00014%2F1482172116765&h=3fcdf7e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161220/s00014/1482172116765</a> <br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】美國藥廠再爆出藥物定價過高爭議。《金融時報》昨報道，Impax Laboratories藥廠以884美元（約6900港元）出售一個療程兩粒的杜蟲藥，價格較英國同類藥貴200倍。 <br />\n<br />\n1.6美元仿製藥停售 藥廠獨市 <br />\nImpax Laboratories出售的蟯蟲藥Mebendazole每粒442美元，一個療程需要服食兩粒，在英國相同藥物一包4粒售6.99鎊，即每粒1.75鎊（約17港元）。這藥物在美國為處方藥，但在英國於一般連鎖藥房有售。 <br />\nMebendazole最早於1970年代起用於治療蟯蟲及其他寄生蟲病，被世衞列為必須藥物，在一些發展中國家每粒只售低於1美仙。現時蟯蟲每年影響全球2億人，在美國每年有多達4000萬人感染。 <br />\n<br />\nMebendazole仿製藥（generic drugs）在2011年前在美國只售約1.6美元（約12港元），生產商Teva之後停售，未有解釋原因。Impax於今年4月以Emverm品牌推出Mebendazole，成為美國唯一生產該藥的藥廠。 <br />\n<br />\nImpax未有回應事件。 <br />\n（金融時報）"},{"pid":"96aa45d4a9004a7406cb2bd98070628d16719fec","tid":51305,"uid":13382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:29:57.000Z","msg":"專利權唔係成個世界都通用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   點解英國可以有彷制藥ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a89f1bbe7a66d8f7d2b4fecea2388dcc4623ee","tid":51305,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>專利權唔係成個世界都通用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   點解英國可以有彷制藥ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n20 年專利過咗啦"},{"pid":"e8816a772b798cfe655549ee5cd23d6b32769565","tid":51305,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:00:22.000Z","msg":"生產商Teva之後停售，未有解釋原因。<br />\n<br />\n其實你反組譯再用其他方法做藥都可以避開專利."},{"pid":"c69e845500d63301022c49613b662b8bf3afbe99","tid":51305,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"美國個醫療制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他處方藥都好貴"}]}